rt/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=01&hitYear=2016&termGbn=week|title=2016\ub144 01\uc8fc\ucc28 Download Chart|work=Gaon Chart|publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association |accessdate=September 13, 2017|language=Korean}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Lifted (CL song)|Lifted]]\"\n| 2016\n| \u2014 || 94 || 31 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"7\" {{N/A}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Rewind\"\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2019\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 4\n| rowspan=\"6\" |''In the Name of Love''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Done\"\n| 154 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 3\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Paradox\"\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"+PARADOX171115+\" did not enter the [[Gaon Digital Chart]], but debuted and peaked at number 192 on the Gaon Download Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=49&hitYear=2019&termGbn=week|title=2019\ub144 49\uc8fc\ucc28 Digital Chart|accessdate=December 27, 2019|website=Gaon Music Chart|language=ko}}</ref>}} || \u2014 || \u2014 || 7\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"I Quit\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 9\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"One and Only\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 13\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|\"THNX\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 16\n|-\n| align=\"center\" colspan=\"14\" style=\"font-size:8pt\"| \"\u2014\" denotes recordings which were not released in that country or failed to chart.<br>\"*\" denotes charts which did not exist at the time of release.\n|}\n\n====As featured artist====\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"7\" | Peak positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:12em;\" | Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Gaon Music Chart|KOR]]<br><ref>Gaon Digital Chart\n*{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gao